{"tid":1203664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Hi! 香港人，醒下啦，無用嫁。","createTime":"2019-06-11T13:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T03:59:42.000Z","uid":258055,"like":367,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"d4725e80f21460309f0b01789f43ec8c1b83691b","tid":1203664,"uid":258055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:08:34.000Z","msg":"文宣無用。你有無幫手翻譯 ，有無盡力推有用既資訊，有無派傳單，有無簽曬所有聯署，身為KOL既你地又有無出過post?<br />\n<br />\n遊行無用。你有無出黎遊行，有無盡力留守到最後（即使無衝），你有無盡力叫你身邊所有朋友出黎？<br />\n<br />\n衝無用。你有無衝過，有無提供資源比敢衝既人，有無捐過錢比為被捕者提供法律支援既團體?<br />\n<br />\n罷工無用。你會唔會罷工，敢唔敢同老闆講係為左香港所以唔番工，如果有人咁樣比人炒左你地又會唔會經濟援助佢?<br />\n<br />\n就係因為每一個人都覺得自己做既無用，最後先會得到無用既結果呀！<br />\n<br />\n你可以做既野：<br />\n<strong>URGENT</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1) 勇武</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202707/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202707/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2) 想呼籲各位香港人，為抗爭者略盡綿力，一齊盡量着黑衫黑褲黑袋戴黑口罩。為各位身攜物資嘅抗爭者作掩藏</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203261/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203261/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3) 識急救</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1201568/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1201568/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4) 提供物資</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1199767/page/1 \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1199767/page/1 </a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5) 和理非: 警方表示明早政總外可集會</span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202945/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202945/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6) 有車既: 告士打道汽車嘉年華</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202042/page/10\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202042/page/10</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">7) 有朋友俾左份名單，有無人今晚想睇樓？</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202590/page/1?post=3\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202590/page/1?post=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8) 和理非非既你唔該轉場去美國領事館</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203232/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203232/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">9) 認真組織一次罷工罷市</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1195880/page/26\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1195880/page/26</a><br />\n<br />\nMODERATE<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">10) 有drone既, 幫手影低金鐘高空佈防情況</span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203410/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203410/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">11) 良好市民: 十八區投訴違例泊車</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203348/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203348/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">12) 幫手推及Share: 【 突發】信已經陸續ready，今晚8:30前我地要幫港共官員同建制派取消外國護照</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202439/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202439/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">13) 幫手推及Share: [突發]香港警犬將被禁止進入台灣 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203236/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203236/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">14) 幫手推及Share: [突發]環球時報總編輯：若香港內地化 中國會失去多彩的一面<br />\n </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203446/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203446/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">15) 提款「反送中」</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203348/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203348/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">16) [強積金終於有用]將香港股票基金轉做外國股票基金</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1200527/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1200527/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">17) 捐款比為被補者提供法律支援既星火同盟: 不是梁天琦，沒人關注，幫手 請不要消費旺角義士 可找星火同盟 送信送餅送煙及捐助</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/681850/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/681850/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">18)【集氣】全球聯署反送中簽名 唔好俾保皇狗拎嗰八十萬打飛機</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202187/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202187/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">19) 簽!!! 聯署北歐商會罷工</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203331/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203331/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 20) 突發！罷市行動已經超過1000間公司響應<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1201630/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1201630/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">21)發起聯署罷工嘅公司/公會</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1202532/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1202532/page/1</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">22)［反送中］白宮聯署</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1195226/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1195226/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">23) 鐘意玩野既, Forward支持反中亂港既偽人上Facebook / Wechat : 勁廢：我再講一次，我沒有去</span><br />\n[/red]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1201618/page/1 \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1201618/page/1 </a><br />\n<br />\n就咁數都20幾樣野，當你唔衝都仲有最少10樣野可以做，你無做齊就唔好再同人講無用! <br />\n<br />\n醒下啦 香港人! 你做既每一樣野都係有用架!"},{"pid":"4de5cc4433b8723a720993b19b8b4236efdfe90a","tid":1203664,"uid":258055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"自推 大家幫幫手"},{"pid":"872d449070620f07a8495547b86ab4a32bd4511e","tid":1203664,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a026130a9bb615b1fce3e66700681cc75edc3eb","tid":1203664,"uid":258055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cited